name: Search in View Window for Out Duty/Tour

testSteps.description: 1: Search in View Window for Out Duty/Tour ({parentTab=Leave Management, childTab=View Request Status, outDutyPeriod=03 Oct 2022, tab=Out Duty/Tour})

children.description: Given User is logged into MIS
When User is on MIS Home Page
When User clicks on "View Request Status" sub tab of "Leave Management" tab
And Click on View Out Duty button
Then Verify "Out Duty/Tour Request Detail" Window appears
When User Enters "03 Oct 2022" period in search box for "Out Duty Details" tab
Then Verify "03 Oct 2022" Period is filtered for "Out Duty Details" tab
